Meg Foster https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meg_Foster 0 Margaret "Meg" Foster (born May 10, 1948) is an American actress who had roles in the TV miniseries version of The Scarlet Letter and the films Ticket to Heaven, The Osterman Weekend, and They Live among many other projects.
